trans-unit.source: Defines the interface that receives workflow instance creation, execution, and termination status information from a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.DebugController"></xref> object running inside the workflow host application.
trans-unit.target: Definierar det gränssnitt som tar emot arbetsflödet instans skapas, köra och avslutning statusinformation från en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.DebugEngine.DebugController"> </xref> objekt som körs i arbetsflödet värdprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] This interface is implemented by a .NET remoting object hosted by the debugger.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Det här gränssnittet implementeras av ett .NET remoting-objekt hos felsökningsprogrammet.
